  O    5.651241   5.651241   1.593000
  O    8.019759   8.019759   1.593000

! 2x denser than SCF k-mesh for smooth DOS
K_POINTS automatic
  8 8 12  0 0 0

HUBBARD (ortho-atomic)
  U Sn-4d 4.0
  U O-2p  0.0
